============== -*- outline -*- ==============

   Renesas White Hawk SDK ROM Writer
   for Windows/TeraTerm

2022/08/23	Kuninori Morimoto <kuninori.morimoto.gx@renesas.com>
=============================================
-------------------------------
* Preparation
-------------------------------
**  TeraTerm

	You need "TeraTerm". See here and get it

		https://ttssh2.osdn.jp/index.html.ja
		https://ttssh2.osdn.jp/index.html.en

-------------------------------
* How to use ? (v3.6.0 or later)
-------------------------------

	You can use TeraTerm Macro which is included on

		R-CarSDK_Startup_Guide_xOS3_ADAS_xxx.zip
			teratermmacro/Flash_Bootloader_V4H.ttl

-------------------------------
* How to use ? (v3.0.1)
-------------------------------

**  [step1] connect Serial between PC and Board

	see
		[Serial connection]
		${renesas-bsp-rom-writer}/board/v4h_whitehawk/README

**  [step2] prepare ROM

	see
		[How to get ROM]
		${renesas-bsp-rom-writer}/board/v4h_whitehawk/README

**  [step3] Start TeraTerm and Open Macro

	[Menu] - [Control] - [Macro]
	Open macro file
		${renesas-bsp-rom-writer}/board/v4h_whitehawk/windows/sdk_writer.ttl
